Feature: Listing sites
  In order to administer my sites
  As a user
  I need to be able to list those sites.

  Background: I am authenticated
    Given I am authenticated

  @vcr site-list-empty.yml
  Scenario: Listing a user's sites when they haven't any
    When I run "[[executable]] site:list --fields=name,id,plan_name,framework,owner,created,memberships,frozen"
    Then I should get the warning: "You have no sites."
    Then I should see a table with rows like:
    """
        Name
        ID
        Plan
        Framework
        Owner
        Created
        Memberships
    """
    And that table should have no rows
    And I should not get: "[[test_site_name]]   11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111   Sandbox   wordpress   United States    11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111   2016-08-16 22:09:01   11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111: Team   false"

